<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help - SafeNest</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@200..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
    * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

body {
    font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    font-optical-sizing: auto;
    
    font-style: normal;
    background-color: #111;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 20px;
}

header h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5em;
    color: #f1675c;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.help-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #222;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

section {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

h2 {
    font-size: 1.8em;
    color: #f1675c;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
    font-size: 1em;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding-left: 10px;
    position: relative;
}

ul li::before {
    content: "•";
    color: #f1675c;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    position: absolute;
    left: -20px;
    top: -2px;
}

.help-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    background-color: #f1675c;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.help-btn:hover {
    background-color: #f14d3c;
}

strong {
    color: #f1c40f;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    body {
        padding: 10px;
    }

    header h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
    }

    p, ul li {
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Help</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="help-section">
        <section class="faq">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>How do I create an account?</strong> – You can create an account by clicking the "Sign Up" button on the login page and following the instructions.</li>
                <li><strong>How do I reset my password?</strong> – Click "Forgot Password" on the login page and follow the prompts to reset your password.</li>
                <li><strong>How do I access healthcare guidance?</strong> – Navigate to the "Healthcare" section where you’ll find health tips and resources specifically curated for teenage girls.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-support">
            <h2>Contact Support</h2>
            <p>If you need further assistance, please reach out to our support team. We’re here to help you with any issues you may encounter.</p>
            <button class="help-btn">Contact Support</button>
        </section>

        <section class="safety">
            <h2>Safety Resources</h2>
            <p>At SafeNest, your safety is our top priority. Please visit our <a href="#safety-guidelines" style="color: #f1675c; text-decoration: underline;">Safety Guidelines</a> page for essential tips on staying safe online and offline.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
